title: Far-left environmental groups conducted internal Biden admin trainings, documents show
description: Two environmental groups — the League of Conservation Voters and Climate Power — have conducted at least one internal training session for Biden administration appointees.
author: Thomas Catenacci

title: ChatGPT faces mounting accusations of being 'woke,' having liberal bias
description: Users have called out the AI bot ChatGPT over its alleged bias against conservatives and its "woke" positions, from politics to transgender ideology to obesity.
author: Joseph Wulfsohn
